# ✅ Commit format (project policy)
# - Start every commit subject with ONE emoji.
# - Emoji must relate to the change.
# - Do not repeat the same emoji in two consecutive commits.
# - 🚫 Forbidden emojis: :lipstick: and :sparkles:
# - 🚫 Never add Co-Authored-By trailers or AI attribution lines.
# - Keep subject concise and technical.
#
# Examples:
# ♻️ refactor: split overview into section components
# 🐛 fix: align story bubbles with timeline curve on resize
# 🔧 chore: update roadmap status for home section 2

🙂 <type>: <short technical summary>
